總佔成佣金: (-1*總上下數)*自身佔成率: ● Total Share Commission: (-1*Total Win/Loss)*Myself Sharing Rate
總洗碼佣金: 總洗碼數*自身轉碼率: ● Total Rolling Commission: Total Rolling* Myself Rolling Rate
洗碼佣金成本: 總洗碼佣金*自身佔成率: ● Rolling Commission Cost: Total Rolling Commission * Myself Sharing Rate
下線佔成佣金加總: 指下線的佔成佣金數合計: ● Total Downline Sharing Commission: The sum of all downline’s sharing commissions
下線洗碼佣金加總: 指下線的轉碼佣金數合計: ● Total Downline Rolling Commission: The sum of all downline’s rolling commissions
佔成佣金: 總佔成佣金-下線佔成佣金加總: ● Sharing Commission: Total Share Commission - Total Downline Sharing Commission
轉碼佣金: 總洗碼佣金-下線洗碼佣金加總-洗碼佣金成本: ● Rolling Commission: Total Rolling Commission - Total Downline Rolling Commission - Rolling Commission Cost
已付佣金: 指已經收到的佣金: ● Commission Paid: The commission that you already received.
應付佣金: 佔成佣金+轉碼佣金: ● Commission Payable: Sharing Commission + Rolling Commission
